    "The self-attention is shown in Fig. 4d and operates as follows:",
    "Here, W K, W V, and W Q are the key, value, and query parameter matrices, respectively; I E is the Transformer input; and 1",
    "is the scaling factor, d k = 4.",
    "The outputs generated by the self-attention mechanism correspond one-to-one to the inputs.",
    "In this study, a \"class token\" vector x class is introduced as additional input to start the prediction process."
